      • answerOf

        public java.util.Map<UnknownParameter,java.lang.Double> answerOf(InverseMethodEnum inverse,
                                                                 int n)
                                                          throws java.io.IOException
        Example, if you want to get an answer of CG1.
        inverse → CG, n → 1 Returning Map key is an unknown parameter.
        パラメータ:
        inverse - used solver
        n - the number of used eigen vectors for the answer
        戻り値:
        Map of answer values
        例外:
        java.io.IOException - if an I/O error occurs

      • bornOf

        public Trace bornOf(BasicID id,
                    InverseMethodEnum method,
                    int n)
             throws java.io.IOException
        If the born waveform already is computed and in a file then, read and return it. If not, this method computes a born waveform and returns it and write in a certain folder.
        パラメータ:
        id - of the target raypath
        method - of inversion
        n - number of eigen vectors(SVD) or CG vectors (CG) or...
        if it is 1 and method is CG then CG1
        戻り値:
        Trace of Born
        例外:
        java.io.IOException

      • createBorn

        public void createBorn(InverseMethodEnum method,
                       int n)
                throws java.io.IOException
        Computes born waveforms of the answer by using n basis vector in the method for all time windows. This method also creates 'eachVariance', 'eventVariance', 'stationVariance' (.txt)
        パラメータ:
        method - to solve an equation
        n - the number of used basis vector
        例外:
        java.io.IOException - if an I/O error occurs
